        "text": "The metaphor perhaps means \"A wise man's sense is in its place, ready to help and protect him; but a fool's sense is missing when it is wanted, and so is useless.\" ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "",
        "children": []
      }
